title: Her Dad Is Being Tinder Swindled?!
description:
Her dad started looking for love again on Tinder after her mom passed away. He matched with a "fitness model" but has yet to meet her in person even though he's given her money for plane tickets.
She knows her father is being scammed but doesn't know how to break the news to her father. Any advice?
